<br>
But anyway, I'll be starting him up sometime this weekend once I get my gear sold in the bazaar and buy some enchanter stuff.  If you'd like to maybe hunt together, or start our characters together (untraditional high-elf/dark-elf alliance would be interesting) just let me know.  I love roleplaying and staying in character when I'm not in trader mode.  Send a tell ingame to Geron.  Hopefully I wont be afk. :-)<br>
<br>
Good luck in whatever you decide.  I hear that once you get to the higher levels and join a guild or make some friends, your less likely to reroll.  Ha, thatll be the day. :-P<br>
