<br>
If you do get a hankering to try out another race/class and you don't wanna shell out the extra cash for another account (I sure don't), try the character out on one of the other servers.  Any of the other servers (not FV and not Sullon Zek) let you have eight character slots to play with per server... lots of room for experimentation there.<br>
<br>
I tried out a bard recently on Maelin Starpyre and almost rerolled Muddy... but in the end I found that I didn't like twisting songs so much.  Not enough to ditch my favorite little coward Iksar, anyway.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><br>
