 <br>
So you won't see the end game. Big frickin' deal. Seen Dulak's Harbor yet? Cobalt Scar? Poked a dragon lately?<br>
<br>
Levitated around Freeport? You'd be surprised at what you'd find walking on top of things instead of running in the streets. Gone to the Plane Of Growth (as a Tunare Worshipper) or talked to your god (if you're an Iksar going to Plane of Fear?).<br>
 <br>
The world is huge. I haven't explored half of it,and I've played since the server started. Part of the nice thing about sticking to and working up a character is being able to see the world. Sure,you may never see Plane of Earth. But you can see Tranquility,Nightmare,Disease,etc etc....<br>
